Changes in TeleGNOME 0.3.2
==========================

 * Fix incorrect description of paging-enabled key.
 * Migrate from gnome-doc-utils to yelp-tools.
 * Port away from gnome-common.
 * Stop using deprecated ACLOCAL_AMFLAGS.
 * Migrate from intltool to Gettext.

Translations:
  cs (Marek Černocký), de (Mario Blättermann), es (Yolanda Álvarez Pérez),
  hu (Balázs Meskó, Gábor Kelemen), oc (Cédric Valmary), pl (Piotr Drąg),
  pt_BR (Rafael Fontenelle), sr (Мирослав Николић), sr@latin (Мирослав
  Николић), sv (Anders Jonsson, Josef Andersson)

