Changes in TeleGNOME 0.3.0
==========================

 * Add Italian teletext channel.
 * Rewrite in Vala.

Translations:
  de (Mario Blättermann), es (Daniel Mustieles), it (Guido Trentalancia)

Changes in TeleGNOME 0.2.1
==========================

 * Don't reset current-channel to the first configured channel on startup.
 * Port from libgnome and libgnomeui to less-deprecated equivalents, mostly
   GResource and GtkUIManager.
 * Port from gtk_timeout_* to GLib equivalents.
 * Port from GtkCList to GtkTreeView and friends.
 * Port to new (as of GTK+ 2.4) GtkToolbar API.
 * Port from GdkDrawable to Cairo.
 * Port to GTK+ 3.
 * Basic port to GtkApplication.
 * Port menu action handling from GtkUIManager/GtkAction to GAction/GMenu.
 * Port widget construction code to GtkBuilder.

Translations:
  de (Mario Blättermann), pl (Piotr Drąg)

Changes in TeleGNOME 0.2.0
==========================

 * Build cleanly with -DGSEAL_ENABLE.
 * Port from GnomeVFS to GIO.
 * Port from gnome-config to GSettings.
 * Add some more default channels.
 * Add missing call to gdk_pixbuf_loader_close that caused TeleGNOME to be
   unable to load some images.

Translations:
  bs (Samir Ribic), ca (Toni Cama), el (MarMav, Mel Argyropoulou), en_GB
  (Bruce Cowan), eo (Kristjan SCHMIDT), fr (Claude Paroz), he (Yaron
  Shahrabani), hu (Gabor Kelemen), id (Andika Triwidada), lv (Rudolfs
  Mazurs), nb (Kjartan Maraas), pl (Piotr Drąg), pt (Pedro Albuquerque),
  pt_BR (Antonio Fernandes C. Neto), ro (Daniel Șerbănescu), ru (Leonid
  Kanter), sl (Matej Urbančič), sr (Мирослав Николић), sr@latin (Мирослав
  Николић), sv (Anders Jonsson), tr (Necdet Yücel), uk (Daniel Korostil), vi
  (Lê Trường An), zh_CN (Aron Xu)

Changes in TeleGNOME 0.1.1
==========================

 * Fix build where GtkType != guint (Debian #479740).
 * Clean up many uses of deprecated GNOME APIs, although there are still a
   few difficult ones left.
 * Add Categories field to .desktop file, so that it shows up in a
   reasonable place in menus.

Translations:
  cs (Marek Černocký), da (Joe Hansen), de (Mario Blättermann), el (Μάριος
  Ζηντίλης), es (Jorge González), gl (Antón Méixome), pl (Piotr Drąg), sl
  (Matej Urbančič), sv (Daniel Nylander)

